        <p>
            <strong class="our">PERSONALITY DEVELOPMENT</strong> <br>
            A well-rounded personality is built on the back of all-round grooming. Being the future citizens of a
            diverse country, it is essential that these children uphold our rich cultural values. We endeavour to
            cultivate these values within our global learners through cultural meets, art competitions, music and dance
            competitions, and much more. At i skool, every child is given a platform to hone and enhance their
            talents, pursuing them simultaneously with academics.
        </p>
        <p>
            <strong class="our"> DIGITAL LEARNING</strong> <br>
            To usher in a new era of world-class education, i skool has adopted a technology-driven approach to
            studies. The schools have replaced textbooks with trendy tabs for students from class five to seven. This
            learning technique not only makes children adept in the use of technology but also reduce the load of study
            materials to be carried every day.
